You can jump to a file located in a deeply nested directory
by pressing Ctrl+Shift+N and typing several characters of the enclosing directories and filename.

Use either a slash or a backslash as a delimiter.

通过按下 Ctrl+Shift+N 并且键入子目录与文件名的几个字符，你可以跳转到一个很深的子目录中的文件
使用斜杠 或者 反斜杠 来作为分隔符号

demo: /idea_tips
好处：不用刻意记住 文件的所属目录,节省脑力